content:
Hi Dr. Grove,

Thank you for taking the time to review my message. I understand you might be busy, so I wanted to follow up and see if you would be interested in discussing the counseling and psychiatric opportunities available at Televero Health.

If you're available for a call, please feel free to schedule a time that works best for you using my Calendly link: <https://calendly.com/bailey-baker-1/30min>

Alternatively, if you know of any colleagues who might be interested in such opportunities, I would greatly appreciate any referrals.

Looking forward to hearing from you.

Best regards,
Bailey
